        "TileImage": "$($repository 9833e86e-7aba-4a32-9096-f02e73b9e554).Image",
        "Description": "FROM: Diana Burnwood\rTO: Tobias Rieper\r\rGood afternoon, 47. Enjoying your vacation?\r\rBad news, however. The FRANCHISE is now back, and is reconstructing itself back to its former glory before your confrontation back in &apos;06. The organization has set their eyes on you for some time; and now they strike.\r\rFor their first move, they have sent several spies to Thailand, disguised as staffmembers at the hotel you are staying. Apparently, they are oblivious to your countenance.\r\rHappy hunting, 47.",
